cinnamon.engine.utils

Interface Identifiable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BodyComponent, ComponentManager.Component, GameObjectManager.GObject, HealthComponent, ImageComponent, ImmutableMesh, ShaderManager.ShaderProgram, TextureManager.Texture

    public interface Identifiable

    Describes instances of a class as being identified with an id and a version. The id identifies a class' instance against all other instances at any given time while version specifies the state of the instance that is desired to be identified. The latter is used to determine whether an instance is still in a desired state.

    There are two invariants:

    • id is never <= 0 or infinity and is used by only one instance at a time
    • if an instance's version changes, the new version has never before been used by the instance
